{"tid":227303,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我愛既唔係你既錢","createTime":"2017-05-03T05:37:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-03T14:58:08.000Z","uid":62320,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f0d89b4ba7339dcbec29992ccaf96cf0cfa5faed","tid":227303,"uid":62320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T05:37:32.000Z","msg":"當一個有錢既扮窮撚<br />\n女人知道就會話：我愛既唔係你既錢 <br />\n<br />\n當一個窮撚扮有錢<br />\n女人知道就會話：雖然我愛既唔係你既錢 但你呃我 我地分手啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果金錢轉處女呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當一個處女扮非處<br />\n男人會話：我愛你唔係因為你個處<br />\n<br />\n當一個非處扮處女<br />\n男人會話：我同你一齊唔係為左食你隻豬 但你呃我 我地分手啦<br />\n<br />\n其實好多例子男女都一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過人總是睇唔到自己做緊自己鬧緊人既野<br />\n<br />\n利申：男 預左被屌<br />\n因為連登係女人是原罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65cbfc3e73f561b7711179f0ee70fc87e5b36e7b","tid":227303,"uid":62320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T09:02:57.000Z","msg":"錢啊臭雞"},{"pid":"67083d8ffcb5f57aff97bc28bfce92687d3a95d3","tid":227303,"uid":62320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T09:43:02.000Z","msg":"你雞黎架咋"},{"pid":"109d98cb3fcd949411380a7d1dacf4908053401f","tid":227303,"uid":62320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T14:58:08.000Z","msg":"雞，全部都係雞"}]}